@page "/"

<PageTitle>Overview — Privestio</PageTitle>

<section class="page-shell hero-panel" data-testid="home-hero">
    <div class="hero-copy">
        <span class="eyebrow">Offline-first personal finance</span>
        <h1>See your money clearly, not just your transactions.</h1>
        <p>
            Privestio brings accounts, imports, and categorization into a single workspace with a calmer, more
            deliberate interface.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
            <FluentAnchor Href="/accounts" Class="button-link button-link--primary">View Accounts</FluentAnchor>
            <FluentAnchor Href="/import" Class="button-link button-link--secondary">Import Transactions</FluentAnchor>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-metrics" aria-label="Key product highlights">
        <FluentCard Class="metric-card metric-card--primary">
            <span class="metric-card__label">Workflow</span>
            <strong>Accounts, rules, and imports</strong>
            <p>Built to keep onboarding and recurring cleanup in the same place.</p>
        </FluentCard>
        <FluentCard Class="metric-card">
            <span class="metric-card__label">Default posture</span>
            <strong>Private and self-hosted</strong>
            <p>Designed for people who want direct control over financial data.</p>
        </FluentCard>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="page-shell content-grid">
    <FluentCard Class="surface-card feature-card">
        <span class="eyebrow">Accounts</span>
        <h2>Track every balance with less friction</h2>
        <p>Add banking, credit, investment, property, and loan accounts with a consistent form flow.</p>
        <FluentAnchor Href="/accounts" Class="inline-link">Open account list</FluentAnchor>
    </FluentCard>

    <FluentCard Class="surface-card feature-card">
        <span class="eyebrow">Import</span>
        <h2>Map files once, reuse the workflow</h2>
        <p>Preview files, inspect errors, and save mappings so repetitive imports take less effort.</p>
        <FluentAnchor Href="/import" Class="inline-link">Go to import</FluentAnchor>
    </FluentCard>

    <FluentCard Class="surface-card feature-card">
        <span class="eyebrow">Rules</span>
        <h2>Keep categorization logic visible</h2>
        <p>Edit rule priority and JSON conditions in a layout that reads like an operations surface instead of a raw
            form.</p>
            <FluentAnchor Href="/rules" Class="inline-link">Manage rules</FluentAnchor>
        </FluentCard>
    </section>
